@startuml activity-retake-test.puml
title Retake Test Service - Activity Diagram

start

:Enter previous test number;
:Retrieve previous test result;

if (Previous test failed?) then (Yes)
  :Create new retake application;
  :Link retake application to original application;
  :Pay retake service fee and test fee;
  :Schedule new test appointment;
  :Display appointment confirmation;
else (No)
  :Reject retake request;
endif

stop
@enduml